yTime":"2018-09-26T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"排到第8個射啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:41:23.000Z","msg":"可能佢地覺得拜利同鐘師要排 10 同 11 先叫後 D"},{"pid":"ee9d9f79d7755300e398b33a25ae31f94b7c19ce","tid":837100,"uid":103947,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"呢個柒頭都係算啦<br />\n乜柒都瀨<br />\n好撚怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b159d86a3eb4f4d82e76ef1ebe8128919e4fa0","tid":837100,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:47:03.000Z","msg":"輸波搵野瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede9dfae52fca9a9fb64f2547b65cc9ae6e28e2f","tid":837100,"uid":74957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"英冠級數中堅都射得入<br />\n你d貴價中堅就有麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57de2167749f3b0c42c7b2b3ed3474cdd4a6e87e","tid":837100,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"cls咁講野<br />\n屌你球員點會有心機幫你踢"},{"pid":"587db4179d96b153b7ca10d532b15473f6d2ce75","tid":837100,"uid":96894,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"aef56b07b8a141a3751d3b5b86f9d7a76348f388","tid":837100,"uid":10249,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"跟啲咁既老細 點會有信心踢波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"比賽前 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=kfSNCAAQUomQqF8ClgZlJkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=faf1d3a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 體育】周二英格蘭聯賽盃第 3 圈曼聯主場對打比郡，周六聯賽在奧脫福失威的紅魔自然想以一場勝仗來討回球迷的歡心，而今年英聯盃的新賽制亦十分符合領隊摩連奴的胃口。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴：「我喜歡盃賽，喜歡淘汰賽那種一場定生死的感覺。我享受盃賽的壓力，球迷也樂在其中吧。今年起 90 分鐘打和的話，不會有 30 分鐘加時，會直接射十二碼分勝負，那時候就要看彩數了，這樣亦能增加爆出冷門的機會，令賽事更加刺激。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我是贊成取消加時的，加時真的非常熬人，尤其是對要踢歐洲賽的球隊來說。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n比賽後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://881903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F881903.com&d=kfSNCAAQUomQqF8ClgZlJkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=510eead4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">881903.com</a>】摩連奴：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聯賽盃改制和波後直接踢十二碼是對強隊不利，如果有 30 分鐘加時，強隊通常都可以勝出。</strong></span>」"},{"pid":"f9f569f358c8eb88c9fd1c5109a04f5af31083c5","tid":837100,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"587db4179d96b153b7ca10d532b15473f6d2ce75","tid":837100,"uid":96894,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"aef56b07b8a141a3751d3b5b86f9d7a76348f388","tid":837100,"uid":10249,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"跟啲咁既老細 點會有信心踢波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"比賽前 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=kfSNCAAQUomQqF8ClgZlJkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=faf1d3a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 體育】周二英格蘭聯賽盃第 3 圈曼聯主場對打比郡，周六聯賽在奧脫福失威的紅魔自然想以一場勝仗來討回球迷的歡心，而今年英聯盃的新賽制亦十分符合領隊摩連奴的胃口。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴：「我喜歡盃賽，喜歡淘汰賽那種一場定生死的感覺。我享受盃賽的壓力，球迷也樂在其中吧。今年起 90 分鐘打和的話，不會有 30 分鐘加時，會直接射十二碼分勝負，那時候就要看彩數了，這樣亦能增加爆出冷門的機會，令賽事更加刺激。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我是贊成取消加時的，加時真的非常熬人，尤其是對要踢歐洲賽的球隊來說。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n比賽後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://881903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F881903.com&d=kfSNCAAQUomQqF8ClgZlJkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=510eead4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">881903.com</a>】摩連奴：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聯賽盃改制和波後直接踢十二碼是對強隊不利，如果有 30 分鐘加時，強隊通常都可以勝出。</strong></span>」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}